    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a fantastic ride and is still in really solid, reliable shape! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, and it\u2019s truly ready to hit the road with its next owner today. It\u2019s perfect for anyone who wants a dependable vehicle without any fuss. I\u2019ve loved every mile in this beauty, and I\u2019m sure you will too\u2014come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
