    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left to give! It\u2019s been well-maintained and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver without the new-car price tag. I\u2019m super excited for its next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
