    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S features the high-revving 3.8L M97 flat-six, delivering a linear power band and visceral acoustic profile. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement with precise synchromesh performance. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the chassis maintains exceptional lateral stability and composure through high-load apexes. Recent preventative maintenance includes an upgraded IMS bearing and a fresh rear main seal to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. While the exterior shows honest road-going patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, and the throttle response is instantaneous. This is a driver\u2019s car, optimized for those who prioritize mechanical feedback and analog engagement over showroom perfection.",
